---
title: Hearty Beef & Hidden Veggie Pie with Filo Pastry & Spinach
description: Follow the scent of baked filo pastry pie to the dinner table. Cut a slice for yourself to enjoy the hidden veggies like carrot and celery, cooked in a tomato based beef filling. Go on, we know you want another slice, we sure do!
